com.rohanclan.cfml.parser
Class ParseMessage

java.lang.Object
  com.rohanclan.cfml.parser.ParseMessage
Direct Known Subclasses:
ParseError, ParseWarning
public class ParseMessage
extends java.lang.Object

A message to be reported to the user. This is intended to be the base class for all other messages that are reported to the user. Clients may create instances of this class. It's not an abstract class.

Author:
Oliver
